name: EnterDAO
additional_notices: Kindly be aware of liquidity-related risks. This notice is not directed at any project in particular, and is more of a cautionary reminder.

description.en: EnterDAO is a an initiative, which grants voting rights to the $ENTR holders. It is founded with the mission to build products enabling new markets within the metaverse economy such as marketplace for renting/lending metaverse land and client used for browsing/entering multiple metaverses from a single application.
